Quickstrike:



Quickstrike crossed his arms and leaned against the wall. "Yeah," he said, 
mentioning about Shredder. He's had the worst luck while in this war. He had 
never gotten on anyone's good side ever since he was brought back on-line. 
Certainly Hell Beast's troops. He was still nervous around Megatron.

He lowered his head and closed is eyes. Maybe it was time to calm down. 
Temper like his couldn't be good for him.

After several seconds, Quickstrike listened in, thinking he'd heard a 
banging going on in the base. He opened his eyes and looked around.

"Ya hear somethin'?" he asked Mantella.
